summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Jones Avenue Northwest from West 65th Street to West 75th Street et al in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing under Ordinance No. 18655, creating Local Improvement District No. 1756 Prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
